title: How the teenage #CEO of #PinkPalmPuff started a viral #fashion brand. #TikTok

author: Business Insider
description:
On this episode of "Well Spent," cohosts Katie Notopoulos and A. C. Fowler discuss the viral $89 Pink Palm Puff hoodie that teens are clamoring for online. They talk to 17-year-old CEO Lily Balaisis about the strategies she used to get her clothing line to succeed, and why her brand took off when so many others fail. Casey Lewis, a trend expert, also breaks down how going viral on TikTok can make businesses more successful among Gen Z and Gen Alpha.
